{"tid":2347714,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"分享收集一年被破壞既政治橫額","createTime":"2020-12-31T08:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T13:50:03.000Z","uid":33875,"like":194,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"f5773497ab6f89cf68e24f955933f972a70df490","tid":2347714,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"抗爭高峰期搭上區議會選舉，政治宣傳橫額掛滿整個香港，破壞亦係歷來最頻密。經過罷鐵、黎明行動，上年十月左右，維修好部舊單車代步，原來新界有好多地方好容易就踩到去，從此，踩單車記錄各式橫額成為每日活動。<br />\n<br />\n第一張收藏品係一位區議員朋友被燒穿大頭既橫額，亦成為電話簿聯絡人張相。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/cgWQ92n/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FcgWQ92n%2Fimage.png&h=52146583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n拍攝、篩選、執圖後，成為一張正式大頭相，或者相中人可以考慮下屆參選用嚟做大頭相。如果仲有下一屆選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">鎅刀類：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1mDz1kf/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F1mDz1kf%2Fimage.png&h=d75cd6f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有唔少作品出於呢位區議員朋友。扎根馬鞍山多年，腳毛留得多，橫額亦掛唔少。結果有人鎅開第一張，剪碎第二張，跑出第三張。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/X3s7Wks/pjB6dDP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FX3s7Wks%2FpjB6dDP.png&h=c57adab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n割爛橫額相對大部份手法，最為方便快捷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/J3Rqznf/OK7Av16.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FJ3Rqznf%2FOK7Av16.png&h=5c1e0005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n選舉經費所限，橫額如果有辦法修補就盡量修補，而最簡單方法就係用寬身膠紙痴返好佢，不過手勢唔好就好容易上下移位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rxKqfM7/92NnmTy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FrxKqfM7%2F92NnmTy.jpg&h=98c143eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相對知名既候選人，針對性眼位落十字兩刀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/mCZTN2y/JmkNCQN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FmCZTN2y%2FJmkNCQN.png&h=43725efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有種比較有效率既會係臉旁直落一刀，再用手橫撕，成塊面皮撕落嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LQYgXyd/ptPDaRf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FLQYgXyd%2FptPDaRf.png&h=f873befd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n並唔係所有被破壞橫額都有人留意到，並唔係每位候選人都有足夠人手及時修補。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/KxsRQf6/zgJVyzB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FKxsRQf6%2FzgJVyzB.png&h=2be5a54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者原材料，即係塊面已經唔見咗一半，點痴膠紙都無用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/VgKSg02/32cu9U5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FVgKSg02%2F32cu9U5.png&h=876a0756&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n甚至唔止一半。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/nC0VXmy/AZECoSN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FnC0VXmy%2FAZECoSN.jpg&h=d349dc10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個可以畫幅太陽眼鏡比佢。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/DRkJkS3/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FDRkJkS3%2Fimage.png&h=4bea8b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n應該基於成本考慮，有人會選擇印張A4紙補返上去。只係佢比較不幸，轉頭又再被鎅爛。"},{"pid":"c1ac03be95380d948ea206a608b2aef115d26614","tid":2347714,"uid":33875,"like":74,"dislike":1,"score":73,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"large\"><span class=\"gold\">貼紙類：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/1YcJgDY/GjbzNGp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F1YcJgDY%2FGjbzNGp.png&h=ce48840a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上年香港文宣平面設計百花齊放，當中仲有作品攞埋獎，橫額上亦被貼上各陣營文宣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/FBNYGhH/lUDHLnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FFBNYGhH%2FlUDHLnB.jpg&h=523931d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/h2y81qW/EgsGFpv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fh2y81qW%2FEgsGFpv.jpg&h=c20e2e5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時分唔清邊個陣營既人，用邊個陣營文宣貼去對方橫額。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/MMFMKBF/Is0bvU7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FMMFMKBF%2FIs0bvU7.jpg&h=f7348baf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一般膠紙膠水尚且易撕，後期有人出動AA膠，甚至自製麵粉漿糊，擲走亦留有痕跡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tLv38JT/8K9LDlU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FtLv38JT%2F8K9LDlU.png&h=3783bad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比文宣更順手，就係街邊廣告招紙。隨手係燈柱偷一張，就可以移籍上橫額。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tYdGrjf/tCul6kD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FtYdGrjf%2FtCul6kD.jpg&h=63127820&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LDe8Flv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLDe8Flv.gif&h=8439df20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n層樓要貶值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/pj01yF8/hw0yVvx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fpj01yF8%2Fhw0yVvx.jpg&h=ea1b6647&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有人好努力撕走過，又將殘骸貼返上去<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/Kq6rCkD/e8qoht3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FKq6rCkD%2Fe8qoht3.jpg&h=fdbd0e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比文宣、街招更就手，就只有，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/gJg2MjN/RtZrDLp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FgJg2MjN%2FRtZrDLp.jpg&h=071e5e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印花，惠康係唔係無哂印花得yuu？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/cLmWkJ6/04pAcHF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FcLmWkJ6%2F04pAcHF.jpg&h=5e02b29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過當中最心機，應該係有人幫鄧家彪痴返兩條眉。"},{"pid":"b6e4118941445ee861c651001666619970b746fa","tid":2347714,"uid":33875,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T08:59:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">字畫類：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tssRZ87/Pk4CCxL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FtssRZ87%2FPk4CCxL.png&h=03e90164&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肯用筆／噴罐畫畫寫字既，都係心機之作。無論落筆幾隨意、幾簡單，至少相對鎅刀有心思。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/bBtjPt0/i7oqpyD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FbBtjPt0%2Fi7oqpyD.png&h=8d1d6c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n技術性創作，噴走眼鼻口，模糊選民對候選人印象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/dm8qRLC/K5oCY94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fdm8qRLC%2FK5oCY94.jpg&h=d7956098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有藝術創作，港版KAWS。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/tmfcxJH/1YSaAPg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FtmfcxJH%2F1YSaAPg.jpg&h=1bacf352&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n豬鼻，相信係比較年長既創作人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/LJfhCBJ/9Ilk8TQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FLJfhCBJ%2F9Ilk8TQ.jpg&h=2f83247e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個人比較欣賞簡淨有力既作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/f8nhJq1/MxcUWhZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Ff8nhJq1%2FMxcUWhZ.jpg&h=e22c038f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢幅算係少有佳作，貓耳、胡鬚以外，連武器都畫埋比佢。<br />\n記得見到呢幅橫額笑到腳震震咁影相，轉身發現當事人係我後面派傳單。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/BgyYvFG/i7xfYKE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FBgyYvFG%2Fi7xfYKE.png&h=23abf062&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/0mPnzN3/8uE42o0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F0mPnzN3%2F8uE42o0.png&h=94c696d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n噴罐、雙頭筆寫字，亦係熱門手法之一，尤其針對敵對政治營陣字眼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/3YQzDMW/LJNrGLy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F3YQzDMW%2FLJNrGLy.png&h=296f330a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者形容詞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/vsw7v8t/UY64nyL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fvsw7v8t%2FUY64nyL.jpg&h=78baccd2&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/41Mm4P8/H6k7V6R.jpg \" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F41Mm4P8%2FH6k7V6R.jpg%20&h=218c1f10&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/25SkjdF/OubYzig.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F25SkjdF%2FOubYzig.jpg&h=82132a29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三位重量級政界人物出現同一張橫額，而且懸掛係主力接中國旅客既酒店旁，獲題「怀人」兩字。"},{"pid":"d99f342f17fbd9d2122fb1b2f67151214c28cf30","tid":2347714,"uid":18638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fda26bca396d444ee3126ac204db193c9fdf495","tid":2347714,"uid":33875,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:01:15.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\">眼睛類：</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/bFgwPBV/6JsbD5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FbFgwPBV%2F6JsbD5a.jpg&h=27000ae2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有唔少人針對雙眼破壞。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/hXQxfds/MmN9ARk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FhXQxfds%2FMmN9ARk.png&h=04e3eb4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n亦有塗黑雙眼。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/DgCT8Md/Ufgbeox.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FDgCT8Md%2FUfgbeox.jpg&h=b66e1d78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者塗黑再寫字。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/R31MWyk/fxq7wXC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FR31MWyk%2Ffxq7wXC.jpg&h=1f0b1bac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n或者塗黑、寫字，再貼紙。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/dJGtNf4/ZjSlIni.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FdJGtNf4%2FZjSlIni.jpg&h=869992ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一門三傑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/skpvyXp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FskpvyXp.jpg&h=b868d903&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q7ZRYKh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fq7ZRYKh.jpg&h=7b3b0b12&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RLZdMHG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRLZdMHG.jpg&h=604279c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/fpSb5pR/M21C7vQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FfpSb5pR%2FM21C7vQ.jpg&h=5327dfba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86c120b3fb60dcdbfe16565b29ff77f25a522d9c","tid":2347714,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"諗住等樓主出晒搶#2點知俾人捷足先登咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1337f0dae5a1afccf2c9aec35cde0a275e9aa6d","tid":2347714,"uid":312333,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:04:53.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾時再有改圖戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcb5f0539ab8377b00b339f8d9d7dd3b6b6fb18","tid":2347714,"uid":33875,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:09:06.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"large\"><strong>其他：</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/rskKb4h/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FrskKb4h%2Fimage.png&h=2f446493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雙頭黑筆亂畫好常見，鎅兩刀亦偶有發生，煙頭燒面就比較罕見，而三種手法出現係同一張橫額，尤其彌足珍貴。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/9tK5wxz/BOVQ54K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F9tK5wxz%2FBOVQ54K.jpg&h=b207bda8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n嗰日係地下見到比佢嚇到震一震，祝君安好。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/fkp2CsC/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Ffkp2CsC%2Fimage.png&h=270bba06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/BsZNrgF/image.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2FBsZNrgF%2Fimage.png&h=c25bbc75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n邊個角度睇都好似望住自己。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/0Xdz9L7/62-s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F0Xdz9L7%2F62-s.jpg&h=7c5974a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太多事發生係呢張橫額，唔知由邊到開始講，我心目中頭三幅出色作品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/9t1rvxF/101.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2F9t1rvxF%2F101.jpg&h=3e3f0618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有好多收藏品未整理好，亦有好多出名既作品未有機會收集到，例如馬鞍山有班藍絲好鍾意玩屎。希望日後有幸遇到，再同大家分享：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/lyndhursk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Flyndhursk%2F&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJmze9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=a6f94e2e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/lyndhursk/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，預祝大家新年快樂，身體健康，多福多壽。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/b144G2S/Q6T3jl7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ibb.co%2Fb144G2S%2FQ6T3jl7.png&h=5ef5790a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e136892abc75d87006718ff1793e6cf0f4e92ef","tid":2347714,"uid":15345,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:10:25.000Z","msg":"好有心機，留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5023c20aefaf6aaca3dd313ce71981e92b26b0b8","tid":2347714,"uid":127579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:10:36.000Z","msg":"全部沙田既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb419989f773e1ca222cfda2c62003276935b762","tid":2347714,"uid":206594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:10:54.000Z","msg":"欠欠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e0213ebeca3537fc6c0a7d5c66a6d674cd1da5","tid":2347714,"uid":128160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:12:20.000Z","msg":"巴打好畀心機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1413d5deb7b5e8b0e929d24a0f93997574c91b29","tid":2347714,"uid":33875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"86c120b3fb60dcdbfe16565b29ff77f25a522d9c","tid":2347714,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:02:29.000Z","msg":"諗住等樓主出晒搶#2點知俾人捷足先登咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食屎狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/tired.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"係九龍東見過張寫住「食屎狗」既橫額 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282c3c9c1532afb4939dc4a78cc33c5b6453ebee","tid":2347714,"uid":33875,"like":0,"dislike":